extends ../../layouts/default.pug

block main
    head 
       link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;700&display=swap", rel="stylesheet")
    .block-footer(style="height: 500vh") 
        img(src="/images/Koi-community.png", alt="Contact 1" style="height: 550px; object-fit: cover; width: 100%; filter: grayscale(0.7);")
        h1.community-title(style="position: absolute; top: 47%; left: 5%; transform: translateY(-80%); text-align: left; font-weight: Bold; font-size: 4rem;  color: white;") Cộng Đồng Koi Healthy
        .btn-home(style="position: absolute; bottom: 370px; left: 6%; transform: translateY(50%); display: flex; justify-content: center;")
            a.community-title(href='/koi' style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: white; border-radius: 5px; ") Trang chủ
            p.community-title(style="font-size: 1.5rem; border-radius: 5px; padding-left:10px; color: #b9daf8;") / Cộng đồng Koi Healthy
        .content-section(style="text-align: center; padding: 50px;")
        h2(style="font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #333; max-width: 200px; margin: 0 auto; margin-bottom: 10px ") Blog & News
        p(style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;") Eleifend quam adipiscing vitae proin sagittis nisl rhoncus mattis. Sem et tortor consequat id porta nibh venenatis cras. Tincidunt praesent semper. Arcu dui vivamus arcu felis.
